<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="devote-vt">devote <strong><em>vt</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /dɪ'vəʊt/    美 /dɪ'voʊt/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>把...用于；致力于；献身于：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Neighbors <strong>devoted</strong> their spare time <strong>to</strong> helping others rebuild homes.
邻居们把自己的空闲时间用于帮助他人重建家园。</p><footer>2016 北京改</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She <strong>devoted</strong> all her life <strong>to</strong> medical work for Chinese women and children. 
她为中国的妇女儿童医疗事业贡献了毕生精力。</p><footer>人教④ – 1</footer></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="devote-oneself-to">devote oneself to</h3>
<p>1.<strong>献身于；致力于；专心于：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>If you have a job, do devote yourself to it and finally you’ll succeed. 
如果你有一份工作，务必全身心地投入，最终你会成功的。</p><footer>2010 四川</footer></div></div>